          },
          "reviewBody": "The staff are not just imparting academics but also working on developing the all-round personality of a child.\nEach aspect of the child is being assessed by applying various pedagogies, and the creative side of the child is being carved out.\nTeachers not only help students achieve their academic goals; they also help students achieve their non-academic goals. Each individual is in the centre.\nThis school gives various opportunities to the teachers, where they are continuously engaged in learning through workshops and training and updating their competence skills for the future challenges and requirements.",
