          "reviewBody": "I would have loved to give negative ratings if that was possible. Don't waste your money here. It is pathetic school. The quality of teachers is so poor , they not only teach wrong concepts but make sure that whatever correct you have learnt so far should be forgotten like the Maths teacher(Class-6) told \" you have got 10 out of 9\"..and repeated the same thrice when student said 9 out of 10. Hindi teacher knows neither pure Hindi nor English..and has just invented Grammar of her own. In the 2 years of schooling of my brother here they made sure to do all kinds of stuff making irrelevant videos, stupid photos ,audio - video recordings.. except imparting education.\n\nDPSS is making sure that it maligns the name and fame earned by  \"DPS\" .",
